Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然平常有点好色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其实背负着\N破除风穴诅咒的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而一直以来都在追杀奈落的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是感觉到\N和那个人一样的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:25.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:32.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:36.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:44.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:57.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:33.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:46.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在大雪中迷路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸  他发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸他…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有\N可以收容我的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你没地方去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就到我家来住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像雪一样洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好美丽的姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你干嘛突然打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在帮你打蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我之后得修行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就没什么其它特别的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你跟那个女的\N后来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一转眼就过了七年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我还是个\N乳臭未干的小朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  打中了吧\N哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第101话 七年之后的残雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你振作点啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可千万不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚强一点哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个季节怎么会有雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话  能够告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是法师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近附近\N经常有雪怪出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里已经有好几个壮丁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像他这样子突然之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立刻赶去约定会面的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这件事告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止妖怪再出来害人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先去收拾她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这妖气不是太重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位法师看起来这么年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会出事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说起来这个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是个\N皮肤雪白的绝色美女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎每个男人\N看到她就迷得晕头转向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上跟着她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子这里恐怕\N也查不到奈落的线索了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚整理背包时\N从里面翻出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想要带来\N可以跟大家一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果没想到居然给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得是不是受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫做烟火哦!烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这种时候下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  弥勒法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位旅者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在大雪中\N遇到麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问有什么我可以帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  这位姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N你可不可以帮我生个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子已经生下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去抱抱他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去抱抱我们的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所谓无功者饭菜不留嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那几个坏蛋不必留给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  看起来真好吃耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是闻到香味才跑回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为突然下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怪不得觉得这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚跟弥勒法师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他们还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了自然就会回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我跟云母的鱼耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别说那么小器的话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇快过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  珊瑚  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有经过你们的同意\N就自己进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且外面的雪下得那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来吃点野猪肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  这真的很好吃耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是生的耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫报应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看  在雪女还没离开之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们最好还是先待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪女?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种天气只要有个\N年轻的男人在路上走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被一个年轻的姑娘叫住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷迷糊糊的跟着姑娘走之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天就往往会被人发现\N已经冻死在雪地里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这个小姑娘\N一身肌肤像雪一样白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个样子美若天仙的女人哩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都说宁可被冻死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要想办法见她一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下弥勒法师危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚也跟他在一起不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  那大概不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真的一点都不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看弥勒法师\N绝对不会放过那个姑娘的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N要是珊瑚突然出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种情景真不敢想象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N珊瑚一定会宰了弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的话\N以前不知道说过多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是不开窍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个雪女也是在\N奈落下落不明的时候才现身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说她都是只妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就绝对不能够放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去看看马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  我跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你们拿去带在身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是回魂汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊  大家快来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  喝这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是回魂汤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得身体冰冷的时候\N听说喝这个最有效了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这好像有效哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这是\N酒精浓度特别高的烧酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上蝮蛇  蝾螈\N还有毛毛虫浸泡而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  她好像恢复精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子已经生下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去抱抱他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去抱抱我们的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家三口\N一定正开心的享受天伦之乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  一起进去吧  相公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人并不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么要出来到处害人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样抓男人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就是为了\N要吸收男人身上的精气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这些是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相公  就是这些孩子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先进去\N熬点米汤给孩子们喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尿布就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经忘得一干二净了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全都是我帮你生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都…都是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还这么多?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我亲耳听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是法师亲生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  这小子\N也到了该纳税的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能这么定下来\N也是件好事不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪随便说几句\N你们别全当真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖气是从里面传出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上破了这个结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好…乖乖啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好…乖乖啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!别把鼻涕擤在我的衣服上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!我的锡杖不是你们的玩具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:12:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我喂与作喝点米汤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有舍松的尿布湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有待会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要唱歌给小虎听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哄他乖乖睡觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  乖乖啦  别再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  好不好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  马上帮你换尿布哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宝宝快睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以在那边尿尿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厕所在这边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你一个人照顾他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为母亲\N谁不会亲自照顾孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多孩子\N难道全都是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子的家\N都被战火烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个一生下来\N就不得不离开他们的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常捡这些孩子回来照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久而久之就变成了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们几个\N全都是可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这好像是…\N弥勒法师的歌声喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不负责任的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他也懂得疼自己的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有间大屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得好熟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖…乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是乖宝宝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶快健康长大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  好乖  好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好乖  好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子弥勒法师中了幻术了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快醒醒吧  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖…乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面几位来者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不准通行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧  雪豹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气这么冷\N四肢当然不容易伸展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把四魂之玉碎片抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死妖怪  今天让我来收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这家伙这么不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀啊  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖哦  乖乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好像有点吵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群野狗在雪地迷了路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上派人把它们赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝宝们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就很清醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己仔细看看  这也叫清醒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天休想逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长得和那个人那么像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我所认识的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以其实我也不想\N对你这么的粗鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿呀  怎么这么不顺利啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让它闪开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可恨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明心地那么的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么偏偏要诱捕那些男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且加害他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界太可恨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨我自己活在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下屠刀才能够立地成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙\N怎么突然变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们最怕热气跟火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那就看我的狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不管用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以利用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我陪你过两招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是另一只雪怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信刚刚那个雪怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有附身在这个灵魂上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个灵魂\N属于一个被卷入战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且丢了性命的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N她一直在寻找那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因不幸而离开人世的\N那些小孩的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至一直照顾着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信这个女人的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被雪怪给控制住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想战国时代的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该活得很艰辛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话又说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始当她告诉你\N替你生了孩子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么想都不想就相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是有\N做过什么见不得人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师\N是为了帮助可怜的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会故意假装中计吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为法师\N怎么可能会犯下这种错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是一只蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该继续上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那位姑娘真的好像喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那天帮助\N年纪还小的我的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位小雪姑娘…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在世界的某个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着幸福快乐的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是残雪…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:15.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:24.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:34.22,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:44.22,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:49.20,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:54.12,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:23:01.52,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:08.07,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:12.25,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:19.50,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:29.52,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:41.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
